{"tid":679162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七煞斬債仔　反遭30人打爆缸 收錯風撞正「大佬」賀壽 人強馬壯冇得走","createTime":"2018-05-26T15:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T18:07:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd6e70d54d0f0b9005c20408c34833f6ad004a2","tid":679162,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401802&d=%2FFDl4tNWdydqFIjJ58siVzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e0dbec17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F20401802&h=9dd55bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180526/20401802</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月26日 <br />\n<br />\n七煞斬債仔　反遭30人打爆缸<br />\n收錯風撞正「大佬」賀壽<br />\n人強馬壯冇得走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/00001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F00001.jpg&h=1082b6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■西貢前晚發生黑幫廝殺案，七名刀手伏擊疑欠債目標時，反遭對方同門圍毆，其中數人圖坐車逃走時遭對方駕私家車、客貨車及拖車夾擊追撞。鄭文輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】西貢黑夜發生如電影般血腥暴力又具喜劇感的黑幫廝殺案。黑幫「和勝和」七名刀手，前日深夜接到指令，分乘三車到西貢，目標是要伏擊一名欠下400萬元不還的另一黑幫水房（和安樂）小頭目，未料對方當時原來剛出席完「大佬」壽宴，小頭目遇襲後，約30多名同門即撲出反擊，將刀手重重包圍追打，又以拖車追撞對方座駕阻止逃走，其中四名刀手被打至血流披面，有人更要跳海逃生，最終警方到場控制場面，拘捕四名受傷刀手，而遇襲小頭目亦受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄭文輝　潘志能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，案中有四名男子（21至30歲）被捕，他們分別頭、胸、手腳受傷。被斬傷的26歲姓黃男子則手腳受傷，亦送院敷治。警方指雙方均有黑社會背景，案件列傷人案，交東九龍總區反黑組跟進，並追緝其他涉案人士，包括三名在逃刀手。<br />\n<br />\n這宗「斬人反被斬」的大混戰昨日成為城中熱話。消息指，有人行動前疑收錯風，只得悉要追斬的姓黃目標男子會在西貢一間酒樓出現，以為是「簡單任務」，未料卻遭對方30多名同門反包圍追打，落荒而逃。原來黃剛參加完其大佬、水房前坐館「肥威」的生日宴，肥威昨天生日，前晚在西貢一海鮮酒家筵開三席，30多名門生到場祝賀，事件中肥威並沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被斬小頭目負傷躲殘廁<br />\n<br />\n事發於前晚11時許，和勝和七名刀手分乘三輛車到達西貢翠塘路一間酒家外，當發現目標黃某踏出酒家時，當中四人戴口罩手持牛肉刀落車趨前向黃追斬，黃中刀受傷，且戰且退，大呼救命，並負傷跑至附近殘廁躲避。<br />\n<br />\n在酒樓內的同門聞訊撲出，各人手持木棍及垃圾桶作武器包圍追打施襲刀手，現場殺聲震天，一片混亂。刀手不敵反遭打至頭破血流，立即跳上停泊在附近露天停車的接應車輛欲逃離現場，其中一輛白色七人車成功逃脫，<br />\n一輛寶馬則失事撞向花槽石壆，車上各人乘亂棄車而逃；但一輛銀色七人車則遭對方駕駛拖車、私家車及客貨車夾擊追撞，車上四人落車逃走但遭眾人追趕圍毆，其中一人跳落海游向一舢舨逃命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大批警員接報到場控制場面，當場拘捕四名受傷刀手，其中一人被發現滿面披血坐在岸邊一艘小艇上，另一人則頭破血流攤坐路邊。遇襲姓黃男子亦受傷，事後分批被送院敷治。警方稍後在白沙灣碼頭尋獲相信是逃脫刀手所坐的白色七人車。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有消息亦指肥威近月曾向海鮮檔收取陀地費時與人爭執，以及追討欠債發生糾紛，警方亦會追查兩者是否與西貢斬人血案有關連。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/00001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F00001.jpg&h=1082b6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■寡不敵眾，其中一刀手滿面披血攤坐路邊。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=fdf5e5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■另外兩名刀手分別被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/26la3p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F26la3p05.jpg&h=dd36b248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有一名刀手為避圍毆，跳海逃生獲救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/26la3p09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F26la3p09.jpg&h=8a99a707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■水房前坐館「肥威」前晚在西貢一酒家筵開三席賀生日，他在大混戰中沒受傷。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n高院成景點　內地網教偷拍攻略<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「熱心巿民」現場主動爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「熱心巿民」現場主動爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n大佬「肥威」門生傳欠四百萬街數<br />\n<br />\n水鬼隊落海蒐證<br />\n<br />\n【黑幫大混戰】勝和水房西貢開拖 警方總共拘捕11人"},{"pid":"5d11f78f3e4eec1c05d50d1781427811214fa844","tid":679162,"uid":27024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"成班低能仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0130c8fd97b2b0ebb5e892e98e7e3dc940f8d4","tid":679162,"uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180526/large/26la3p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180526%2Flarge%2F26la3p02.jpg&h=d7f3bb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寡不敵眾，其中一刀手滿面披血攤坐路邊。讀者提供圖片"},{"pid":"9960954a1ae26192f3f2886cf0f84a6651fd707e","tid":679162,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"ON9仔咁都收錯風"},{"pid":"450303b609ccb8df6aac9f28f8b9fb90d64aaa10","tid":679162,"uid":30055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"大佬生日搞單咁嘅嘢條友以後都唔使有運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ae624f8f5e2d4399fafd077f1fac4cae132557","tid":679162,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"架車應該自己唔係阿公"},{"pid":"d5326334b5a3e4c45c9d7e517b19162d026a17ec","tid":679162,"uid":13250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"咁肥走去做刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔俾人斬死算執返條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcb5bdfea3121351ca4000d0167f56d7bc9498a","tid":679162,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"跳海 <br />\n<br />\n諗起浩南 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bc55d1fef70cbbeb67701b70c0a241042d30b8","tid":679162,"uid":75137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"前坐館生日=&gt;延開三席"},{"pid":"552c67c4e1d85f77c461a6f7454cd6368c186114","tid":679162,"uid":75137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85bc55d1fef70cbbeb67701b70c0a241042d30b8","tid":679162,"uid":75137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"前坐館生日=&gt;延開三席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"筵"},{"pid":"d75ffefc4093639f020659817e7e645258a9a6e7","tid":679162,"uid":33424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"睇少D古惑仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8711aafe039a76a37c5eb944edd6c54e74e2f86","tid":679162,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"收數王個肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd805fc687d9390e8d943fd23bdd8e9bc3a69366","tid":679162,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30996b0347640a78fad674111e46832b376d31e1","tid":679162,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd805fc687d9390e8d943fd23bdd8e9bc3a69366","tid":679162,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c5bdd2f185443ffb1fc438895f47e01ff69c91","tid":679162,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd805fc687d9390e8d943fd23bdd8e9bc3a69366","tid":679162,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁今次斬唔到佢斷手斷腳算佢好彩<br />\n希望下次再俾人斬過"},{"pid":"82ccfffdb95b4960395087bcc0afa0c3ecb8fd98","tid":679162,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"146e5e08257cbe529553549b6c66ac86d1abff1c","tid":679162,"uid":67635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T18:07:36.000Z","msg":"條肥仔個肚咁似女人生完bb d肚紋"}]}